@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<h2>About Us</h2>

<section class="about-section">
    <div class="section-header">
        <h3>Our Story</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="section-content">
        <p>Welcome to [Company Name], where our passion for [industry] and commitment to [core values or mission] drives everything we do. Our journey started in [year], and we've been growing ever since with a focus on quality, customer satisfaction, and innovation.</p>
        <p>At [Company Name], we believe in providing [products/services] that make a difference. We strive to deliver excellence through every interaction, and our team is dedicated to ensuring that every customer feels valued and heard.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="mission-section">
    <div class="section-header">
        <h3>Our Mission</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="section-content">
        <p>Our mission is simple: to [describe your core mission in one to two sentences]. We aim to [insert company goals or long-term vision]. With sustainability, community, and quality at the heart of everything we do, we aim to make a lasting impact on our industry and beyond.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="team-section">
    <div class="section-header">
        <h3>Meet The Team</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="section-content">
        <p>Our team consists of dedicated professionals who bring a wealth of experience, creativity, and passion to the table. Together, we work toward achieving our vision and helping our customers succeed.</p>
        <div class="team-gallery row">
            <div class="team-member col-md-6 text-center">
                <img src="team-member1.jpg" alt="Team Member 1" class="team-image">
                <h4>John Doe</h4>
                <p>Founder & CEO</p>
            </div>
            <div class="team-member col-md-6 text-center">
                <img src="team-member2.jpg" alt="Team Member 2" class="team-image">
                <h4>Jane Smith</h4>
                <p>Chief Operating Officer</p>
            </div>
            <!-- Add more team members as needed -->
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="contact-section">
    <div class="section-header">
        <h3>Contact Us</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="section-content">
        <p>If you have any questions or would like to learn more about our products and services, feel free to reach out to us.</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Email: <a href="mailto:contact@company.com">contact@company.com</a></li>
            <li>Phone: (123) 456-7890</li>
            <li>Address: 1234 Main Street, City, Country</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</section>